            ",[3798,4030],"\n                  The average company uses 76 different security tools. They don&#39;t talk to each other, they generate thousands of false positives, and when something real happens — it takes days to figure out what.\n                ",[3798,4030],"\n                  The average company uses 76 different security tools. They don&rsquo;t talk to each other, they generate thousands of false positives, and when something real happens — it takes days to figure out what.\n                ",[4272,4479],"\n                  SEQYO changes that equation. We give companies a unified intelligence layer — powered by AI, backed by experts — that&apos;s as fast and collaborative as the threats they face.\n                ",[4272,4479],"\n                  SEQYO changes that equation. We give companies a unified intelligence layer — powered by AI, backed by experts — that&lsquo;s as fast and collaborative as the threats they face.\n                ",[4272,4479],"\n                  SEQYO changes that equation. We give companies a unified intelligence layer — powered by AI, backed by experts — that&#39;s as fast and collaborative as the threats they face.\n                ",[4272,4479],"\n                  SEQYO changes that equation. We give companies a unified intelligence layer — powered by AI, backed by experts — that&rsquo;s as fast and collaborative as the threats they face.\n                ",[6430,6506],"Decades of combined experience protecting the world&apos;s most critical systems.",[6430,6506],"Decades of combined experience protecting the world&lsquo;s most critical systems.",[6430,6506],"Decades of combined experience protecting the world&#39;s most critical systems.",[6430,6506],"Decades of combined experience protecting the world&rsquo;s most critical systems.",[1987,2033],"\n                Let&apos;s secure\n                ",[1987,2033],"\n                Let&lsquo;s secure\n                ",[1987,2033],"\n                Let&#39;s secure\n                ",[1987,2033],"\n                Let&rsquo;s secure\n                ",[2215,2395],"\n                Whether you want a demo, have a security emergency, or just want to learn how SEQYO can help — we&apos;re here. A real human will respond within 2 hours.\n              ",[2215,2395],"\n                Whether you want a demo, have a security emergency, or just want to learn how SEQYO can help — we&lsquo;re here. A real human will respond within 2 hours.\n              ",[2215,2395],"\n                Whether you want a demo, have a security emergency, or just want to learn how SEQYO can help — we&#39;re here. A real human will respond within 2 hours.\n              ",[2215,2395],"\n                Whether you want a demo, have a security emergency, or just want to learn how SEQYO can help — we&rsquo;re here. A real human will respond within 2 hours.\n              ",[5027,5077],"Fill out the form and we&apos;ll get right back to you.",[5027,5077],"Fill out the form and we&lsquo;ll get right back to you.",[5027,5077],"Fill out the form and we&#39;ll get right back to you.",[5027,5077],"Fill out the form and we&rsquo;ll get right back to you.",[5246,5263],"I&apos;m interested in",[5246,5263],"I&lsquo;m interested in",[5246,5263],"I&#39;m interested in",[5246,5263],"I&rsquo;m interested in",[5006,5188],"\n              Whether you&apos;re a two-person startup or a multinational enterprise, SEQYO adapts to your environment, your compliance requirements, and your risk appetite.\n            ",[5006,5188],"\n              Whether you&lsquo;re a two-person startup or a multinational enterprise, SEQYO adapts to your environment, your compliance requirements, and your risk appetite.\n            ",[5006,5188],"\n              Whether you&#39;re a two-person startup or a multinational enterprise, SEQYO adapts to your environment, your compliance requirements, and your risk appetite.\n            ",[5006,5188],"\n              Whether you&rsquo;re a 